{
  "stem": "2226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we went to a shochet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The shochet killed the-- the goose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we all eat it for Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then the-- the Russians come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So a few days later, the Russians come in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's when we got with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I actually didn't see the Germans before when I got back to Poland, because I smuggled the-- the border back from-- like the Russians straightened out the border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Germans were already [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Russians took it back, because they [INAUDIBLE] half Poland and half-- half Russian-- half, I mean, German took it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I came to [INAUDIBLE], I couldn't go farther.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And from over there, they were all together with small children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But what-- what-- what we going to do over there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I smuggled-- smuggled the border back to Poland twice to bring my mother back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody wants to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they all got-- they all went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I meant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got from Ciechanow to Auschwitz when I back with mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- no, there was a [? known ?] place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was not a [? burg ?] like in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that city was around the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't make it, because they demolished all the Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They demolished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so where are they gonna put us?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they put in-- in the barns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- like for the whole city, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They start-- so we lived in those places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As many as could go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you mean, how many?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who counts?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had over 100 in our yard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Poland?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, in this barn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole time after '42 when they-- when they evacuate us too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
